-- Only named floats are shown; rare 1-2 profile cliffs (0.125/0.300/0.350/0.430) are skipped.
-- hit_frac / ap_scale are averages across profiles that share that exact armor
-- value (chip is never blended across other tiers). `name` is the short class
-- label used when MCM column_headers = "names".
